          <tr>
            <td width="70%" style="vertical-align: top;">
               <p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px;">A COMMUNITY ENTERPRISE INSPIRED BY THE VISION OF VIDYAKSHETRA</p>
               <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #666;">Thank you for your support!</p>
